stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ActiveChat: 创建 chat 线程
    [*] --> ActiveWorkflow: 创建 planning / troubleshooting 线程
    [*] --> Completed: 创建 knowledge / learning / safety artifact 线程

    ActiveChat --> ActiveChat: /messages 多轮对话
    ActiveChat --> Completed: 导出对话记录

    ActiveWorkflow --> ActiveWorkflow: 继续追问
    ActiveWorkflow --> Planned: 生成 contract
    Planned --> ExecutionInProgress: 步骤开始 / 检查点确认
    ExecutionInProgress --> ExecutionInProgress: 持续推进 / 上传附件
    ExecutionInProgress --> Blocked: 步骤 blocked / 检查点 failed
    Blocked --> ExecutionInProgress: 重置后继续
    ExecutionInProgress --> Completed: 全部步骤 done 且检查点通过
    Planned --> Completed: 直接导出方案

    Completed --> Completed: 恢复查看 / 导出
